自19世紀起[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]就有[[俗語|俗語]]說明苹果和健康的關係：“[[一天一苹果，医生远离我|一天一苹果，医生远离我]]”（{{lang-en|An apple a day keeps the doctor away}}）<ref name="A Pembrokeshire Proverb">{{cite journal|last=Phillips|first=John Pavin|date=1866-02-24|title=A Pembrokeshire Proverb|journal=Notes and Queries|publisher=Oxford University Press|volume=s3-IX|issue=217|page=153|url=http://nq.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/s3-IX/217/153-d|accessdate=2009-02-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829162245/http://nq.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/s3-IX/217/153-d|archivedate=2009-08-29}}</ref>。初步的研究表示，蘋果可以降低罹患[[结肠癌|结肠癌]]、[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]和[[肺癌|肺癌]]的風險<ref name="Nutrition to Reduce Cancer Risk">For decreased risk of colon, prostate and lung cancer: {{cite web|url=http://cancer.stanford.edu/information/nutritionAndCancer/reduceRisk/|title=Nutrition to Reduce Cancer Risk|publisher=The Stanford Cancer Center (SCC)|accessdate=2008-08-18|archive-date=2008-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615042347/http://cancer.stanford.edu/information/nutritionAndCancer/reduceRisk/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。蘋果皮含有[[熊果酸|熊果酸]]，在大鼠實驗中可以增加[[骨骼肌|骨骼肌]]及[[褐色脂肪組織|褐色脂肪組織]]，減少[[白色脂肪組織|白色脂肪組織]]，同時降低[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、{{link-en|葡萄糖耐受不良|glucose intolerance}}以及[[脂肪肝|脂肪肝]]疾病的風險<ref>Kunkel SD, Elmore CJ, Bongers KS, Ebert SM, Fox DK, et al. (2012) Ursolic Acid Increases Skeletal Muscle and Brown Fat and Decreases Diet-Induced Obesity, Glucose Intolerance and Fatty Liver Disease. ''PLoS ONE'' 7(6): e39332. {{DOI|10.1371/journal.pone.0039332}}</ref>。依照美國農業部的資料，一份約重242克的蘋果熱量為126卡，含有大量的[[膳食纖維|膳食纖維]]及[[維他命C|維他命C]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/fruits-and-fruit-juices/1809/2 |title=Nutrition Facts, Apples, raw, with skin [Includes USDA commodity food A343] |publisher=Nutritiondata.com |accessdate=2013-01-03 |archive-date=2012-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121228030614/http://nutritiondata.self.com/facts/fruits-and-fruit-juices/1809/2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

